      "date": "2013-05-27 07:10:10.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAndreas, the better solution for that are:\n\n1) Lustre supports UUID completely (2 \"int\" via statfs). Back-port to b2_1 and b2_3? \n\n2) nfs-utils patch for 64bit ino# But I do not know whether it will affected the existing released nfs-utils on rhel5/6.",
