      "date": "2013-05-29 21:09:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nFan Yong,\nrather than disabling the tests, I'd prefer to fix the NFS FSID generation in Lustre.\n\nSince there isn't yet a patch to fix this even on master (AFAIK), I'm OK with landing this patch to b2_1 as a temporary workaround to get testing working again.\n\nThere should be a separate patch that fixes the FSID generation for Lustre, and when it is backported to b2_1 the \"32bitapi\" workaround can be removed (or avoid this entirely if the FSID patch is ready earlier).",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
