        "name": "Jian Yu",
        "email": "yujian@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "yujian"
      },
      "date": "2013-06-13 10:25:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAfter running the tests on more interop combinations, I found this patch broke the interop testing between Lustre b2_1 client and b2_2 server:\n\n Lustre b2_1 client + b2_2 server:\n parallel-scale-nfsv3 passed: https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3be55720-d251-11e2-b1c7-52540035b04c\n parallel-scale-nfsv4 failed: https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3f502322-d251-11e2-b1c7-52540035b04c\n\n Lustre b2_1 client + b2_1 server:\n Both parallel-scale-nfsv3 and parallel-scale-nfsv4 passed:\n https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/bb12ec44-d3bc-11e2-ace1-52540035b04c\n\n Lustre b2_1 client + b2_3 server:\n Both parallel-scale-nfsv3 and parallel-scale-nfsv4 passed:\n https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d5574152-d24c-11e2-a537-52540035b04c\n\n Lustre b2_1 client + b2_4 server:\n Both parallel-scale-nfsv3 and parallel-scale-nfsv4 passed:\n https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/882d0c52-c97a-11e2-8cff-52540035b04c\n\n Should I update the codes as follows?\n\n if [[ $(lustre_version_code $SINGLEMDS) -ge $(version_code 2.2.0) ]]; then\n         CL_MNT_OPT=\"$MOUNTOPT,32bitapi\"\n fi\n \n or\n\n if [[ $(lustre_version_code $SINGLEMDS) -ge $(version_code 2.2.0) &&\n       $(lustre_version_code $SINGLEMDS) -lt $(version_code 2.3.0) ]] ||\n    [[ $(lustre_version_code $SINGLEMDS) -ge $(version_code 2.3.61) ]]; then\n         CL_MNT_OPT=\"$MOUNTOPT,32bitapi\"\n fi\n\n or\n\n if [[ $(lustre_version_code $SINGLEMDS) -ge $(version_code 2.2.0) &&\n       $(lustre_version_code $SINGLEMDS) -lt $(version_code 2.3.0) ]]; then\n         [[ $NFSVERSION = 4 ]] && CL_MNT_OPT=\"$MOUNTOPT,32bitapi\"\n elif [[ $(lustre_version_code $SINGLEMDS) -ge $(version_code 2.3.61) ]]; then\n         CL_MNT_OPT=\"$MOUNTOPT,32bitapi\"\n fi",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
